Feature: US_002 Log In test to the Product Store page

  Scenario: Product Store Log in test as a registered user.

  * As a visitor, you are navigated to the Product Store home page.
  * The destination URL is verified as "Product Store".
  * It is verified that the Log in link in the footer is visible.
  * Click on the Log in link.
  * Username textbox should be displayed on the page that opens.
  * Password textbox should be displayed on the page that opens.
  * Enter user name in Username box.
  * Enter password in Password box.
  * Log in button should be displayed
  * Log in button should be clicked.
  * The Log out link in the footer section should be displayed and successful login should be verified.
  * Close the page.

